commit.message:
Makefile.in (tree-sra.o): Add $(EXPR_H) dependency.

2010-01-22  Steve Ellcey  <sje@cup.hp.com>

	* Makefile.in (tree-sra.o): Add $(EXPR_H) dependency.
	* tree-sra.c: Add include of expr.h.
